title: DAZ3D - Pool Deck Exterior
description:
Pool Deck Exterior is a pool scene with deck chairs and umbrella props. Items load as a full scene Preload. (All objects are separate objs grouped together. So the deck floor, pool water, ladders, umbrellas, fences, and chairs, can all be individually selected to move around, or can be hidden for added versatility with camera angles.) Optimized for Daz Studio 4.9, includes both Iray and 3delight versions.
